Dubai, a tiny desert emirate, is being shaped to become the leisure capital of the oil rich Gulf. Centrepiece of the new Dubai is The Dubai Mall, designed to outstrip all shopping malls. With the largest indoor aquarium, an Olympic sized ice rink, a roller coaster, twelve hundred shops it also has a slogan as brash as its scale: Everything You Desire.
